data.description: Stunning pool home in the desirable gated community of Royal Oaks in Miami Lakes. This spacious property offers a perfect blend of modern upgrades and comfortable living spaces. Four bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, impact windows and doors, remodeled kitchen and bathrooms, high-end appliances, tile floors, vaulted natural wood ceilings that add a touch of warmth and character, spacious bedrooms, and the primary suite offers a tranquil retreat with its own en-suite bathroom and modern fixtures and finishes, a dedicated game room area with a pool table, a two-car garage, a cabana bathroom for easy access from the pool area, and solar panels to help reduce energy costs. The neighborhood offers a peaceful and family-friendly environment, with well-maintained streets and lush landscaping.
